{\pard\intbl\ql {{{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ \\a\\ac(lim,{\i N}{\u8594*}{\u8734*}) \\i \\su({\i i}=1,{\i N}, ){\i f}({\i x}\\s\\do4({\fs15 {\i i}})){\u916*}{\i x}\\s\\do4({\fs15 {\i i}})}}{\fldrslt }}
